original_title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2019 - Jan 16, 2019 Chiba
overview: Fantastica Mania 2019 was a professional wrestling tour, scripted and co-produced by the Japanese New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW) promotion and the Mexican Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre (CMLL) promotion. The tour started on January 11 and ran until January 21, 2019, with shows taking place in Osaka, Ehime, Kyoto, Gifu, Chiba and Tokyo. At Makuhari Messe.
title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2019 - Jan 16, 2019 Chiba
